    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的张先生表示，美联储可以加快利率正常化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/fed-can-speed-up-rate-normalization-jpmorgan-s-chang-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通全球研究部主席 Joyce Chang 表示，未来六个月的路径很清晰，她解释了美联储为何应在年底前实施 100 个基点的宽松政策。（更正了视频和说明中的嘉宾头衔。）（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-15/fed-can-speed-up-rate-normalization-jpmorgan-s-chang-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国零售销售数据好于预期，新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/emerging-market-currencies-hover-around-2-year-high-stocks-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示美国经济具有韧性，令市场对美联储下月大幅降息的预期降温，发展中国家货币削减了周度涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/emerging-market-currencies-hover-around-2-year-high-stocks-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行高管称 ESG 阻力正在减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/deutsche-bank-executive-says-esg-backlash-is-losing-its-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行财富管理部门的一位高管表示，曾引发全球范围内撤离投资策略的反 ESG 情绪浪潮现已显示出减弱的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/deutsche-bank-executive-says-esg-backlash-is-losing-its-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗紧张局势和美国零售销售强劲推动油价止跌两日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对伊朗可能袭击以色列的担忧和美国强劲的经济数据掩盖了持续的需求担忧，油价在连续两天下跌后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 23:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据显示美国经济保持强劲，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于零售支出和劳动力市场数据凸显出全球最大经济体的实力，股市上涨，债市下跌，缓解了人们对美联储可能面临经济进一步放缓风险的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 22:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
